INSERT INTO public.sample_essays VALUES ('810b4377-f773-47a1-b8b9-184de93d8081', '[FORECAST WRITING] Dự Đoán IELTS WRITING TUẦN (11/5-18/5)', 'forecast-writing-du-doan-ielts-writing-tuan-115-185', '<h1 dir="ltr">Dự đoán IELTS Writing Task 1-2 tháng 5 (11/5 - 18/5)</h1>
<p dir="ltr">  </p>
<p dir="ltr">Lưu ý: Dự đoán có bạn trúng có bạn không do số đề random rất nhiều, đây chỉ nên là các đề dùng để tham khảo trước khi thi nhưng AD vẫn mong là các bạn sẽ trúng phần nào đó. Chúc các bạn học tốt.</p>
<p dir="ltr">Nếu bạn cần sample hoặc muốn gợi ý viết nhanh trong 30 phút, hãy sử dụng Chat Bot<a href="https://chatgpt.com/g/g-NfjggXjSs-ielts-prediction-ai"> IELTS Prediction</a> nhé — nó sẽ soạn đúng theo đề bạn sắp thi. Chúc bạn đạt đúng aim trong kỳ thi cuối năm!</p>
<h3 dir="ltr"><strong>TASK 2</strong></h3>
<p dir="ltr"><strong>Environment &amp; Energy</strong></p>
<ol>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Every day, millions of tons of food are wasted all over the world. Why do you think this is happening? And how can we solve this problem?</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">The best way to solve the world‘s environmental problem is to increase the price of fuel. To what extent do you agree or disagree with this statement?</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Fossil fuels, such as coal, oil and natural gas, are the main source for many countries. However, some nations are using alternative energy such as solar power and wind power. Do you think this is a positive or negative development?</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Some people believe that all wild animals should be protected. Others say that few wild animals should be protected instead. Discuss both views and give your opinion.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p dir="ltr"><strong>Education &amp; Youth</strong></p>
<ol start="5">
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Some people think that children should start school at a very early age, but others believe that children should not go to school until they are older. Discuss both views and give your own opinion.</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Students leave high school without learning how to manage their money. What are the reasons and solutions to this issue?</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Many students find it is harder to study at university or college compared to when they were in grade school. Why is this? What are some possible solutions for this problem?</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p dir="ltr"><strong>Globalization &amp; Economy</strong></p>
<ol start="8">
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Some people think that the main benefit of international cooperation is in the protection of the environment, while others believe that the main interest is in world business. Discuss both views and give your opinion.</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Some experts suppose that when a country is already rich, any additional increase in economic wealth does not make its citizens happier. To what extent do you agree or disagree?</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p dir="ltr"><strong>Society &amp; Lifestyle</strong></p>
<ol start="10">
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">More and more people today are spending large amounts of money on their complexions in order to look younger. Why do people want to look younger? Do you think this is a positive or negative progression?</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Towns and cities are attractive places. Some people suggest that the government should spend money putting in more works of art like paintings and statues to make them better to live in. To what extent do you agree or disagree?</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Young people are often influenced in their behaviors and situations by others of the same age. This is called "peer pressure". Do the disadvantages outweigh the advantages?</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p dir="ltr"><strong>Technology &amp; Work</strong></p>
<ol start="13">
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">It was predicted that people living in the twenty-first century would have more free time than ever before because of improvements in technology. To what extent has this prediction come true?</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">It is better for people to be unemployed than being employed with a job they do not enjoy. To what extent do you agree or disagree?</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p dir="ltr"><strong>Sports &amp; Business</strong></p>
<p style="padding-left: 40px;">15. Nowadays, sports is a big business with high earnings for professional sports people and companies involved both financially and in other ways. Is this a positive or negative development for sports?</p>
<hr>
